ITEM 2.06. MATERIAL IMPAIRMENTS
 
On December 16, 2004, Briggs & Stratton Corporation issued a press release announcing that it has taken additional impairment on the trade receivable from Murray Inc.
 
ITEM 9.01. FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS
 
