This Transition Supply Agreement (this "") is made as of February , 2005 (the "") by and between BRIGGS & STRATTON POWER PRODUCTS GROUP, LLC, a Delaware limited liability company (hereinafter referred to as ""), and MURRAY, INC., a Tennessee corporation, on behalf of itself and any of its successors, including any liquidating trust, if any, created pursuant to any plan of reorganization (hereinafter referred to as "").
