(a) . Murray shall comply with all laws, regulations, ordinances and rules that pertain to the manufacture of the Products at its facilities including but not limited to laws, regulations, ordinances and rules regarding or relating to employee working conditions, employment relationships or the termination thereof, and the handling and disposal of environmental and hazardous wastes.
General
 
