(a) . The Company shall pay an arrangement fee to the Arranger for the Arranger's own account, and shall pay an agency fee to the Administrative Agent for the Administrative Agent's own account, as required by the letter agreement ("") between the Company and the Arranger and Administrative Agent dated May 6, 2004.
