RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION
ITEM 2.02.
           
 
On October 20, 2005, Briggs & Stratton Corporation issued a press release announcing fiscal 2006 first quarter results as of October 2, 2005 in the press release furnished as Exhibit 99.1.
 
FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS
ITEM 9.01.
           
 
