 means the date on which all conditions precedent set forth in
Section 5.01
are satisfied or waived by all Lenders (or, in the case of
subsection 5.01(e)
, waived by the Person entitled to receive any applicable payment).
Code
 means the Internal Revenue Code of 1986.
