clause (a)
shall be in the currency in which such Letter of Credit is denominated or other arrangements shall be made so that the Administrative Agent and the applicable Issuing Lender are satisfied, in their sole discretion, that the amount of Backup Support for such Letter of Credit is sufficient to account for currency fluctuations during the remaining term of such Letter of Credit.
