 means the requirement that the aggregate number of creditors (other than Swiss Qualifying Lenders) of B&S AG under all outstanding debts classified as debentures (
Kassenobligation
), including Loans to B&S AG, not at any time exceed 20, in accordance with the Swiss Guidelines.
          
