58
(c)
    
No Existing Default
. No Default or Event of Default shall exist or shall result after giving effect to such Borrowing or Issuance.
Each Notice of Borrowing, and each L/C Application and, if requesting a Credit Extension, L/C Amendment Application, submitted by a Borrower hereunder shall constitute a representation and warranty by such Borrower that, as of the date of each such notice and as of each Borrowing Date or Issuance Date, the conditions in
