promptly, but not later than five Business Days after the date of filing with the SEC, copies of all financial statements and reports that the Company sends to its shareholders generally, and copies of all financial statements and regular, periodical or special reports (including any report on Form 8-K) that the Company or any Subsidiary may make to, or file with, the SEC; and
(d)
    
promptly, such additional information regarding the business, financial or organizational affairs of the Company or any Subsidiary as the Administrative Agent, at the request of any Lender, may from time to time reasonably request.
